00:00:53.920 --> 00:00:58.050
The Handii Hackberry is a 3D printed open
source robotic hand.

00:00:58.050 --> 00:01:02.500
The Japanese company has made the blueprints
and source code freely available and it features

00:01:02.500 --> 00:01:08.860
