Engineers at Harvard have developed a soft
robotic glove to help the disabled grasp objects.

00:02:53.279 --> 00:02:59.719
Designed for sufferers of ALS, muscular dystrophy
and stroke, the glove is soft and lightweight.

00:02:59.719 --> 00:03:03.510
