00:03:12.620 --> 00:03:16.309
A group of chemists and engineers have invented
a neural lace.

00:03:16.309 --> 00:03:21.849
Small enough to be injected, brain cells have
been found to grow around and connect to the

00:03:21.849 --> 00:03:27.010
lace, successfully creating a mechanical connection
into a biochemical system.

00:03:27.010 --> 00:03:31.439
The Neural Lace has only been tested on mice
as of now, but could someday be used to treat

00:03:31.439 --> 00:03:36.650
